title: War of the Roses: She Listens to War of the Roses
description: John found flirtatious texts on his wife Mandy's phone with a co-worker and he confronted her about it and she claims it's nothing.  John doesn't know if he believes her so he wants to do War of the Roses but the problem is, she listens to War of the Roses.  SO Jenny fills in, and we develop a different ploy to try to trick her.
